    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Building a realtime feed]]></title>
    <link href="http://dominicphillips.de/blog/2013/08/09/realtime-feed-with-go-websockets-and-backbone/"/>
    <updated>2013-08-09T22:03:00+02:00</updated>
