<h3>Wiring up the frontend</h3>

<p>We continue in app.js. with some boilerplate code. We&rsquo;re good citizen and namespace our app under the FEED object, so we don&rsquo;t pollute the global namespace. We add a start method that we use to bootstrap our router and views and wrap it inside jQuery&rsquo;s document ready function. We&rsquo;ve also added a global event bus <i>vent</i>, that we can later publish events to.</p>

