<h3>Wrapping it up</h3>

<p>So far we&rsquo;ve laid out the foundation with some boilerplate code, added a &ldquo;catch-all&rdquo; route that proxies most requests to our frontend app and added some frontend libraries. Pretty basic stuff.
In the next post we&rsquo;re going to open a web socket connection and wire it all up with the Feed controller. Thanks for reading, stay tuned.</p>
